title: Pumpkin Burritos
ingredients: ['1 onion, chopped', '1/2 teaspoon each of cumin, paprika and coriander', '1 (200g) tin baked beans', '1 (400g) tin red kidney beans, drained', '250g pumpkin, boiled and mashed', '4 tablespoons mild taco sauce', 'flour tortillas', '3 tomatoes, diced', '1 large avocado, sliced', '200g light Cheddar cheese, grated']
